list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Add Orders feature: Implement `OrderList` component, API support, and integrate with UI
- Created `OrderList` component with filters and enhanced data display. - Updated `dataProvider` to support fetching order data with `getList`. - Integrated Orders resource in `App` routes and `PageMenu`. - Rebranded footer and app bar to "Biidin Admin".

task.summary:
Add initial project setup with Makefile, React files, and basic components
- Created Makefile with package manager detection and essential workflows. - Set up React project structure with index.tsx and basic components. - Added pages like Dashboard, UserProfilePage, and ExchangeKeysPage. - Included utility files and assets (e.g., logo.svg). - Configured ESLint, Prettier, and environment variables.
Fix ExchangeKeysPage: Correct state property name from `runOnServerValue` to `runOnServer`
Refactor ExchangeKeysPage: Enhance `parseBoolean` logic and remove unused `showInFormsValue`. Update WebhookCreate to use English text.
Add `useAuthenticated` to pages for authentication enforcement
Enhance error handling for API requests: add `HttpError` handling in `httpClient` and introduce `safeFetch` utility for robust API calls in `authProvider`.
